Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂與「玫瑰人生」接舷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為取得新的GUNDAM3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那裏等待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中門少佐所率的警務部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對焦急的浦木一行人不屑一顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲點燃了殖民地的推進燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向地球的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下的露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的死迫使妮娜與宿命對決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在浦木為阻止殖民地墜往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以GUNDAM3號機迎向決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}強襲、阻止界限點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙世紀0083
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11月12日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以將殖民地墜往地球為目的的星塵作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可說正漸入佳境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷11時方向有1敵影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球軌道艦隊還不可能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽說有這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去通信室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是阿克西斯艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我艦隊就在後方觀戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善後的事就有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿克西斯的名譽起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能做到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日需要ZION一半艦艇的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如今只以這麼點艦隊進行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塊頭大了點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地大約在月球與地球中間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試作GUNDAM3號機已經接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中立的阿克西斯艦隊則退往後方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸取了一年戰爭的教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是敵人，卻是次漂亮的殖民地墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是GUNDAM3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅憑他一架…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距墜落地球還剩14小時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝敗只在9小時內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就越過阻止界限點了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止界限點？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏被突破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法阻止殖民地那樣的質量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前必須奪取殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並掉轉它的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地的推進燃料還有剩餘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為墜往賈布羅而進行最終調整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第3軌道艦隊在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阻止界限點前方的3-0-2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為迎擊正在集結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕不及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已無話可說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Field！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}I-Field：米諾夫斯基粒子中電磁波流動產生的磁場\N擁有使光束武器偏向的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距殖民地10萬7千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距阻止界限點8小時22分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請許可MS出動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在3號機打開突破口之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉的體力真的能撐住嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會扯上這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在應酬ZION的亡靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從遇上GUNDAM之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束都被這樣彈開的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那以光束為主的機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是阿爾比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請歸艦補給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請歸艦一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差少許就突破第一線了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人無法奪取殖民地的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的問題是敵人何時會在正面出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的地球軌道艦隊大半是薩拉米斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒料到會被刺中軟弱的肋腹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎預料之事經常會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎預料之事經常會發生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是第72戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊將再次展開追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使追不上敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後處理也請交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您剛才說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始武器櫃的交換作業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，我開Stamen出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Stamen：「雄蕊」的意思，與武器庫系統(Orchis)\N合體後便成為RX-78 GP-03D 石斛蘭(Dendrobium)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在戰鬥狀態嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提、提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴密的包圍會使敵人背水一戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，您在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，您想利用這狀況做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡快讓地球軌道艦隊全面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈米托夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止奇怪的策劃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何GUNDAM3號機會交給了阿爾比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能依靠希瑪艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要親手去幹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣少佐您的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那架GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何曾懷著如此激動的心望著地球呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在正面的敵人出現之前打倒GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，距時限還剩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩3小時11分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已沒有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來也不會有援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·巴普爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准許使用小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你立刻離開本艦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想以自己的意志看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方可不會發薪水給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰速5分鐘之後最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪的艦隊太過超前了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別無退路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人，前方有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去啊，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能擴大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球軌道艦隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那排列狀是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交叉隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船不後退？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至界限點的距離！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1萬2百
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩21分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要過了那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些囉嗦的的傢伙也會閉嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是要將我與艦隊做餌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向聯邦搖尾乞憐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓殖民地墜落？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是不墜落？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老傢伙閉嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人突破一線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手不夠用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷MS彈射器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙，時間呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有4分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉沒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Field被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩50秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過阻止界限點了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜往地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓它掉在賈布羅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1軌道艦隊來電
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是迪拉茲艦隊停止戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中止？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是G21
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系統Ⅱ的上部展開完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W11
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請增援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰有誤差
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快展開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人已迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有防止殖民地墜落的秘訣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要加點熱就會「砰」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣也算ZION的將領嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這麼活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些厚著臉皮踞坐在SIDE3的傢伙頤指氣使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有理由我就會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想引導沒有志向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我本身的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被引導到阿克西斯那種邊境之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是生意倒閉之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這獅子身上的害蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動哦，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗軍之將要好好認命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想傷了送給聯邦的土特產哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.50,0:24:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貫徹意志
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今殖民地還在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.02,0:24:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.06,0:24:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏過我的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.05,0:24:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.28,0:24:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我在宇宙中梟首示眾嗎？卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系統在瞄準著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.20,0:24:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別、別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.70,0:24:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.45,0:27:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預    告
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.64,0:27:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛的宇宙覆滿陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.59,0:27:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的時代露出面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.54,0:27:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於殖民地要席捲地球了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.33,0:27:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在這之中恩怨的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.23,0:27:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今，浦木在戰鬥的盡頭見到的是…
